title: Why Grok is first and foremost a disinformation machine
subhed: Grok, the chatbot that has been integrated into the X social network and aims to rival ChatGPT, has recently spread Holocaust denial and false information about the November 2015 attacks in France. It was a reminder that Elon Musk's tool, far from being neutral, was designed to misinform.

title: COP30's unambitious agreement preserves multilateralism but overlooks climate emergency
byline: By Audrey Garric (Belem (Brazil), special correspondent) and Perrine Mouterde (Belem (Brazil), special correspondent)

title: Niklas Frank, a son consumed by hatred for his Nazi father
subhed: Niklas Frank, an 86-year-old former journalist, is known in Germany for his absolute loathing of his father. As a Reich official, Hans Frank, appointed by Hitler in Poland, was among those sentenced to death at the Nuremberg trials, which began 80 years ago.
